author: Ash-kyun
text:
I saw many comments in the chat saying things along the lines of her being tired after 10 to 15 minutes of exercise. What I think many don't realise is that Rushia has bronchial asthma so not only does that mean it fatigues her faster but makes it much harder to breathe even after a short exercise period. People need to be more forgiving to Rushia as it was apparent she was having difficulty with breathing. 

Please don't overdo it in the future Rushia. Your health is the most important thing and I'm sure you don't want to cause much worry to your fans. We all love you Rushia so please try to not do anything that could jeopardize your health. :_ハート::_ハート::_ハート:
